cc:Work.dc:title: Colour Wheel
cc:Work.dc:description: Created by generating a conical 'Full Saturation spectrum CW' gradient in GIMP in a 400x400 image (from point 200,200 to 200,399), scaling to 200x200 (bicubic resampling), importing PNG into inkscape, gaussian blurring (SD=5), then masking to two XORed circles.
